   | id                        | BugId             | see BugId                                                                                                                                      |
   |---------------------------+-------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
   | knownAffectedReleases     | Affected_Releases | This field displays the software releases known to be impacted by this bug.                                                                    |
